  ('pukao-8ec6300d-moex-00087', 'pukao-8ec6300d', 'pukao-8ec6300d-moex-113-156cbda0', 'sub-pukao-8ec6300d-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關網路通訊設備，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["集線器用來把網路實體線路連接，屬於實體層（PhysicalLayer）的設備", "交換器通常是屬於第二層（資料連結層（DataLinkLayer）），可處理網路實體位址", "無線網路存取點（WirelessAccessPoint,WAP），可以把無線網路與有線網路連接在一起", "橋接器（Bridge）可用來連接不同的網路區段，並能依據來源與目的位址，決定封包如何轉送"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:35:42+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9efb7247b3e1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3ae533baf445", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113080", "c": "454", "s": "2604", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "計算機概要", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 34, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "pukao", "civil_category": "電信工程"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('pukao-8ec6300d-moex-00088', 'pukao-8ec6300d', 'pukao-8ec6300d-moex-113-156cbda0', 'sub-pukao-8ec6300d-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '有一種記憶體功能，CPU先檢查它是否存有所需的資料。如果有，直接存取此資料；如果沒有，則存取主 記憶體的資料。此記憶體稱為：', '["輔助記憶體（AuxiliaryMemory）", "堆疊（Stack）", "基本輸入輸出系統（BIOS）", "快取記憶體（Cache）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:35:42+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9efb7247b3e1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3ae533baf445", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113080", "c": "454", "s": "2604", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "計算機概要", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 35, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "pukao", "civil_category": "電信工程"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('pukao-8ec6300d-moex-00089', 'pukao-8ec6300d', 'pukao-8ec6300d-moex-113-156cbda0', 'sub-pukao-8ec6300d-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '任何網頁的內容均是透過HTML的語法所建立，下列關於 HTML的敘述，何者錯誤？', '["HTML檔案是純文字檔", "網頁內容區分成標頭（Head）與主體（Body）兩個區域，主體才是在瀏覽器中間畫面看到的網頁內容", "空白在HTML中是無效的符號", "HTML的標籤名稱會區分大小寫"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:35:42+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9efb7247b3e1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3ae533baf445", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113080", "c": "454", "s": "2604", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "計算機概要", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 36, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "pukao", "civil_category": "電信工程"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('pukao-8ec6300d-moex-00090', 'pukao-8ec6300d', 'pukao-8ec6300d-moex-113-156cbda0', 'sub-pukao-8ec6300d-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '一個網域名稱伺服器（DNS server）收到大量的查詢，其UDP封包表頭中的來源IP位址皆為1.2.3.4，下 列敘述何者錯誤？', '["封包中的來源IP可能是偽造的", "這些UDP封包可能試圖對此網域名稱伺服器進行阻斷攻擊（denialofserviceattack）", "應將1.2.3.4永久列入黑名單", "這些UDP封包可能試圖對1.2.3.4進行阻斷攻擊"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:35:42+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9efb7247b3e1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3ae533baf445", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113080", "c": "454", "s": "2604", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "計算機概要", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 37, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "pukao", "civil_category": "電信工程"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('pukao-8ec6300d-moex-00091', 'pukao-8ec6300d', 'pukao-8ec6300d-moex-113-156cbda0', 'sub-pukao-8ec6300d-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '主張網路服務供應商平等處理所有數據，提供同樣的服務等級，禁止以競爭為由封鎖網站或是服務，係屬 於下列何種資安領域？', '["安全管理技術", "吹哨者保護條款", "網路主權", "網路中立性"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:35:42+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9efb7247b3e1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3ae533baf445", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113080", "c": "454", "s": "2604", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "計算機概要", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 38, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "pukao", "civil_category": "電信工程"}'::jsonb, NULL),
